"37NB-W443D0+4D0 REV:D" is silkscreened on the board.
The FCC test report lists the following additional models as identical.. *Longshine LCS-WR5-2214N1 *Encore ENHWI-N (FCC ID on unit is NOI-W443B) *ViSTOR WFN-44
The power adapter included with the device is a '''DVE''' DSA-12W-10 FUS 12012 (12V, 1A).
